Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:22.37,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&E6E6E6}いい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:24.29,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}{\c&CCCCCC}いや～　しかし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.54,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}{\c&CCCCCC}多分ものすごく迷惑をかけると思うぞ
