Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:50.98,Dial-JPN,,1511,0,0,,{\bord3}{\fad(0,222)}何でだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:55.61,Dial-JPN,,1922,0,0,,{\bord3}{\fad(222,0)}あなたを選んだ私です
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:57.41,Dial-JPN,,0,1111,0,,{\bord3}{\fad(0,222)}もうとまらない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:03:01.62,Dial-JPN,,0,1500,0,,{\bord3}{\fad(222,0)}運命様から決められたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:03.75,Dial-JPN,,555,0,0,,{\bord3}I believe
